  "3183600": {
    "name": "星象迷案 The Zodiac Mystery",
    "steam_appid": 3183600,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/f872aedd8907c8821847a5594fb1d74a.poster.avif?t=1771813865\" width=970 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/f872aedd8907c8821847a5594fb1d74a.webm?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/f872aedd8907c8821847a5594fb1d74a.mp4?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一部神秘的笔记本突然出现在了我的办公桌上，“活人生祭”“恶魔召唤”这些字眼刺得我眼睛发痛。一桩尘封22年的悬案，就这么毫无征兆地再次成为警局焦点。别人都说这是“不可抗力”，可我偏不信这个邪——这世界上哪有推不开的门？档案室的灰尘里，陈年的秘密在纸页间蜷成了团，我偏要耐着性子，将它们一张张抚平；审讯室的沉默里，谎言就像墙皮上长出来的霉斑，我会一寸寸将它们撕开。他们能困住过往所有追查者的脚步，却别想锁住我——这个被执念啃噬、想要揭开一切的我。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/9910fbb25c0bdd4857aa8bda03162887.poster.avif?t=1771813865\" width=970 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/9910fbb25c0bdd4857aa8bda03162887.webm?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/9910fbb25c0bdd4857aa8bda03162887.mp4?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/825bea3ca707c6ca09d5d198d4f12cfb.poster.avif?t=1771813865\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/825bea3ca707c6ca09d5d198d4f12cfb.webm?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/825bea3ca707c6ca09d5d198d4f12cfb.mp4?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入命案现场，我的首要任务是进行系统性排查：任何一处细节都可能藏有关键信息。拿起放大镜仔细检视每个物件的表面纹理、材质特征、以及是否存在异常痕迹，比如细微的划痕、残留的污渍或被篡改的迹象，通过分析这些细节推断其与案件的关联。被害者的尸体是现场最关键的切口：细致观察尸体的姿态、伤口，检查指纹、衣物褶皱等隐蔽部位，寻找可能附着的物证，为后续的案件推理提供依据。这些碎片看似散落无序，实则是拼合真相的密钥。漏掉其中任何一条，都可能让我在后续推理时卡在死胡同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/83183813308d76574bd8194f4b789f18.poster.avif?t=1771813865\" width=970 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/83183813308d76574bd8194f4b789f18.webm?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/83183813308d76574bd8194f4b789f18.mp4?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/65a2f963af072e331fe2e987f3b57b4e.poster.avif?t=1771813865\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/65a2f963af072e331fe2e987f3b57b4e.webm?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/65a2f963af072e331fe2e987f3b57b4e.mp4?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >推开审讯室的门，桌角摊着的档案袋里露出嫌疑人的星座卡片——这是系统给的第一份暗示。我的任务，是从嫌疑人的只言片语里榨出真相。嫌疑人或许会摆出无辜的表情，说着滴水不漏的证词，但每个眼神闪烁、每次手指蜷缩、每句刻意放慢的回答，都藏着破绽的信号。别放过任何反常的反应：当提到被害者的名字时，他是否突然提高了声调？当展示尸体照片时，他的瞳孔是否骤然收缩？这些细微的表情变化，比他说的任何话都更有价值！记住，越是看似天衣无缝的辩解，越可能藏着致命的漏洞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/4cc1708c93db583ef50b3aa7cf348652.poster.avif?t=1771813865\" width=970 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/4cc1708c93db583ef50b3aa7cf348652.webm?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/4cc1708c93db583ef50b3aa7cf348652.mp4?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/c80a7d2d266f655a1284913a0e5039d0.poster.avif?t=1771813865\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/c80a7d2d266f655a1284913a0e5039d0.webm?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/c80a7d2d266f655a1284913a0e5039d0.mp4?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >翻阅人物关系图的瞬间，那些名字像缠绕的蛛网般在眼前铺开——十二个方框里的黑白照片尤其刺目，他们分属十二个不同的星座，死亡日期成了无人能解的谜，就连尸体的埋藏地点都要靠凶手刊登在报纸上的谜题指引才能找到。我的任务，就是扯着这张网的线头，一点点理清楚这些人之间被爱恨浸透的羁绊。有人为爱包庇罪行，有人因恨伪造不在场证明，就连看似无辜的旁观者，身上都沾着没擦干净的秘密。谁是加害者，谁又是受害者？不到最后一步根本无法断定。我必须在这团乱麻中找个突破口，一层层剥开这些被包裹的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/1f399c063ebbf116adcf96a4e9ba4245.poster.avif?t=1771813865\" width=970 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/1f399c063ebbf116adcf96a4e9ba4245.webm?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183600/extras/1f399c063ebbf116adcf96a4e9ba4245.mp4?t=1771813865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，别指望有标准答案！每一处对话分支、每一次筛选证据，都在推开一扇全新的门。我的每一个选择，每一个定论，都将导向不同的终章，让不同的人性，挣扎浮出水面：可能在这个结局里，凶手是被仇恨逼到绝境的可怜人；换条路线追查，却发现他不过是贪婪的囚徒。与其说在找真凶，不如说在看这张关系网的无数种崩裂方式——而我要做的，就是一次次重启这段追查，在不同的选择里踏遍每个分叉路口，让那些隐匿在暗处的惊人秘密，逐个在不同结局里现形。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在这场理性与直觉的角力中，最危险的可能不是谜题本身，而是我正在逐渐动摇的信念——或许，解谜者，本就是谜题的一部分。</strong></p>",
